        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I seriously doubt you'll get a response. You tried to cram too many issues into one letter.</P><P>Personally, I think you should have stuck to our epic.</P><P>It looks retarded, and the effect is, in every sense of the word, useless. If you want a snare, use the 29 darkness. If you want a snare with lots of damage, use the 59 darkness. When you have lich and your only nuke that will stick is a lifetap, mana is meaningless.</P><P><img src="http://members.bellatlantic.net/vze24qqk/public_html/truemara.jpg" border=0><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
